claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: The image displays the header of the Morbidity and Mortality Weekly Report (MMWR) Vol. 71, No. 1 dated August 26, 2022, without any data, figures, or text about vaccine strain matching. does not support the claim because the image contains only the report header and provides no information about Flublok’s antigenic match to WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
